w to instanciate a theme and inject it inside your app","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"image":"ic_theme_intro.png","name":"Preparation of the theme","tutorials":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-2-instanciate-theme"]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In this chapter you will see how you can use your first components provided by OUDS Swift Package"}]}],"image":"ic_component_intro.png","name":"Use of first components provided by OUDS","tutorials":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-3-use-first-components"]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In this chapter you will use original components of OUDS and richer ones"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"image":"ic_component_intro.png","name":"Richer and more original components of OUDS","tutorials":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-4-use-other-components"]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"OUDS is not only about components and themes. It provides view modifiers, typographies and tokens which can be used. You will learn how.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"image":"ic_design_token_intro.png","name":"Typography, view modifiers and tokens","tutorials":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-5-styling-things"]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can have questions and issues, and there are resources online. Let’s see that together."}]}],"image":"ic_unified_ds.png","name":"Go further with more ressources","tutorials":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-6-going-further"]}]}],"kind":"overview","references":{"doc://OUDSThemesContract/tutorials/OUDSThemesContract/tutorial-3-use-first-components":{"type":"topic","kind":"project","url":"\/tutorials\/oudsthemescontract\/tutorial-3-use-first-components","role":"project","estimatedTime":"30min","title":"Use your fir